flowchart TD
    Start([Teacher Login]) --> Dashboard[View Dashboard<br/>Classes & Stats]
    Dashboard --> Choice{What to do?}

    Choice -->|Create| Quest[Create Quest<br/>AI or Manual]
    Choice -->|Monitor| Gradebook[Open Gradebook<br/>View Submissions]
    Choice -->|Analyze| Insights[View Insights<br/>Student Performance]
    Choice -->|Manage| Classes[Manage Classes<br/>View Students]

    Quest --> Publish[Publish to Class<br/>Set Due Date]
    Gradebook --> Grade[Grade Submissions<br/>Question by Question]
    Insights --> Identify[Identify Struggling Students<br/>View Top Performers<br/>Check Mastery Heatmap]
    Classes --> Details[View Class Details<br/>Student Roster]

    Publish --> Monitor[Monitor Progress<br/>Track Submissions]
    Grade --> Feedback[Provide Feedback<br/>Update Gradebook]
    Identify --> Intervene[Plan Interventions<br/>Adjust Teaching]
    Details --> Monitor

    Monitor --> End([Logout])
    Feedback --> End
    Intervene --> End

    style Start fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style Dashboard fill:#10b981,color:#fff
    style Insights fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff
    style End fill:#8b5cf6,color:#fff
